reviewText: OK movie. Not great. VHS tape supposed to be in  almost new but wouldn't play at all on one of my VCR' s and just barely on a second. I could at least watch the movie.
Shannon Tweed is so hot.  I have to work on getting all her movies.

This movie was entertaining sort of soft porn with a plot. Two partners set out to recover money that they lost in a crooked real estate deal. Things lead to murder,romancel and sweet revenge against the crooks.
